But I’m leaving my Christmas stuff up until the new year, anyone else? It brings me so much joy and although I’m happy to clean up my home, I’m sad to see the joy of Christmas go! It was such a good holiday season 🥹❤️

2023, you were one of the best years of my life 🫶🏼 I’m thankful for it all. I spent so much time with my family, my two girls, friends, and just simply being happy. I fell back in love with my body, turned 30 with my husband and truly made some of my favorite memories of all time. Let’s do it again in 2024 🖤
